#: package/contents/ui/config.qml:306
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Crashes/Black screen? Try changing the Qt Media Backend to gstreamer.<br>To "
"recover from crash remove the videos from the configuration using the "
"command below in a terminal/tty then reboot:<br><strong><code>sed -i 's/"
"^VideoUrls=.*$/VideoUrls=/g' $HOME/.config/plasma-org.kde.plasma.desktop-"
"appletsrc $HOME/.config/kscreenlockerrc</code></strong>"
msgstr ""
"發生崩潰或是黑螢幕嗎？請試著將 Qt 媒體後端改為 gstreamer。<br>要從崩潰的情況復原，請在終端機或 TTY 裡用以下指令從設定檔案裡把影片設定"
"移除，然後重新啟動：<br>"
"<strong><code>sed -i 's/"
"^VideoUrls=.*$/VideoUrls=/g' $HOME/.config/plasma-org.kde.plasma.desktop-"
"appletsrc $HOME/.config/kscreenlockerrc</code></strong>"

